contents: We are a God-fearing, determined couple currently surviving a pandemic and long distance together. We’ve been practically together for 5 years and are very eager to get married. Jay made this website for Sammy, to commemorate her first quarter century of life. She’s remarkably beautiful and talented, and I’m so blessed to call her my girlfriend. We have a long way to go, literally in physical distance and figuratively in understanding each other and having a triunal relationship with God. But we’re ready to take the long road, anything feels possible when we are together.
